reviewText: Very good and funny show, if you are a fan of the Police Story series from Jacky Chan, then this is the show for you because of how similar it is.
Quality is not the best, but I am glad to own this on DVD.

I love this package it contains the entire TV series the quality may be poor but its understandable and it's fun!!! Looking to kill some time or enjoy your weekend watching some 80s reto anime this is your deal
